 h Meeting Day 1 as an all-day entry\, the Day 2 rate decision at 14:00 ET\
 , and the minutes release three weeks later at 14:00 ET. SEP meetings are 
 marked on the rate-decision event rather than split into separate entries.
  Schedule from federalreserve.gov.
